@startuml
title 17 - Fluxo Alternativo - Cancelamento Antes do Shipment

autonumber
actor Buyer as Comprador
participant "Marketplace Web" as FE
participant "Marketplace BFF" as BFF
participant "Order Service" as Order
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Fulfillment Center Service" as FC
participant "Payment Platform" as Payment
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
database "Order DB" as OrderDb

Comprador -> FE: Solicita cancelamento
FE -> BFF: POST /api/web/v1/orders/{orderId}/cancel + Idempotency-Key
BFF -> Order: POST /orders/{orderId}/cancel + Idempotency-Key
activate Order
Order -> OrderDb: Verifica pedido e chave idempotente
alt Pedido ainda não possui shipment
  Order -> OrderDb: Marca pedido como Cancelled
  Order -> Kafka: ReleaseInventoryReservationCommand
  Order -> Kafka: ReleaseFulfillmentCapacityCommand
  Order -> Kafka: VoidPaymentAuthorizationCommand
  Order -> Kafka: OrderCancelledIntegrationEvent
  Order --> BFF: 202 Accepted
else Pedido já confirmado ou shipment criado
  Order --> BFF: 409 Conflict
end
deactivate Order

BFF --> FE: Resultado do cancelamento
FE --> Comprador: Exibe status atualizado

Kafka -> Inventory: ReleaseInventoryReservationCommand
Inventory -> Kafka: InventoryReservationReleasedIntegrationEvent
Kafka -> FC: ReleaseFulfillmentCapacityCommand
FC -> Kafka: FulfillmentCapacityReleasedIntegrationEvent
Kafka -> Payment: VoidPaymentAuthorizationCommand
Kafka -> Notification: OrderCancelledIntegrationEvent
Notification -> Notification: Notifica cancelamento

@enduml
